## MSAASampling enum

This enum represents the sampling level to apply to a \[\[MSAARenderPass\]\] instance. At level 0, only one sample is performed, which is like disabling the MSAA pass.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare enum MSAASampling 
```
